			<dataSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples xml:lang="en">The foreground data of raw materials, energy input, and exhaust emissions were obtained from a case study enterprise in Zigong (Sichuan, China), Chuangqi Environmental Protection Building Materials Co., Ltd., which has undertaken the utilization project of WDC used as a raw material for sintered bricks, with an annual output of 30 million bricks. </dataSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples>
